<plot>Heartless parents C.L. Doyle and his wife take two of their older children, Rosebud &amp; Joseph T. Doyle on a family vacation to Alaska, but dump their younger ones, Freddy &amp; Margaret Jean in a Los Angeles foster home. Infuriated by this, Rosebud talks Joseph T. into running away with her so that they can break their younger siblings out of the system, which sparks a manhunt, and an outburst of sympathy among kids everywhere.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?602950</url></doc>
